name: Puffy
description:

Positive Prompts:
(masterpiece), (best quality), HDR, intricate detail

For girls:

1girl, solo focus, skindentation, perfect face, puffy face, beautiful face, big eyes, puffy eyes, perfect eyes, eyelashes, __skin_color__, __eye_color, __hair__

Or

1girl, solo focus, skindentation, perfect face, puffy face, beautiful face, big eyes, puffy eyes, perfect eyes, eyelashes, __popular_character__

Use body parts for full body shot example: chubby body, narrow waist, big pelvis, wide hips

For Negative Prompts:

Make sure you have downloaded the embeddings (EasyNegative, bad-hands-5).

Use nsfw, naked, nude, nipples in the negative if you want clothes on your girls.

Recommanded settings:

  • Steps: 25

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras or UniPC

  • CFG scale: 7

  • Size: 512x768 or 512x512

  • Denoising strength: 0.45

  • Clip skip: 2

  • Hires upscale: 1.5

  • Hires upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp (can be found on huggingface.co)

Future improvement will be made to the model.

Known issues:

  • Third-party hands: I recommend cropping the photo using the Resize Width in the upscaler to avoid third-party hands.

  • Faraway eyes are not good.
